%section.py-20.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8.bg-white
  .max-w-7xl.mx-auto
    .text-center.mb-16
      %h2.text-4xl.md:text-5xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
        Effortless Onboarding: Your Path to Listing in 24 Hours
      %p.text-xl.text-gray-500.mb-6
        Becoming a Wheels on Rent Partner is a seamless process designed for speed and clarity. Our dedicated support team guides you through every step, ensuring you start receiving valuable leads without delay.
      %h4.text-2xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
        Eligibility and Requirements
      %p.text-xl.text-gray-500.mb-12
        To maintain a professional and trustworthy marketplace, all partners must meet the following criteria:

    .grid.grid-cols-1.md:grid-cols-3.gap-8.mb-12
      / Card 1 - Registered Business
      .bg-white.border-2.border-gray-200.rounded-xl.p-8.shadow-md.hover:shadow-lg.transition-all.text-center
        .w-20.h-20.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6{style: "background-color: rgba(58, 99, 99, 0.1)"}
          %svg.w-10.h-10{fill: 'currentColor', viewBox: '0 0 24 24', style: 'color: #3A6363'}
            %path{d: 'M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z'}
        %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
          Registered Business
        %p.text-gray-600.leading-relaxed
          You must be a fully licensed Car Rental Company or Broker/Aggregator.

      / Card 2 - Physical Office
      .bg-white.border-2.border-gray-200.rounded-xl.p-8.shadow-md.hover:shadow-lg.transition-all.text-center
        .w-20.h-20.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6{style: "background-color: rgba(0, 180, 216, 0.1)"}
          %svg.w-10.h-10{fill: 'currentColor', viewBox: '0 0 24 24', style: 'color: #00B4D8'}
            %path{d: 'M10 20v-6h4v6h5v-8h3L12 3 2 12h3v8z'}
        %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
          Physical Office
        %p.text-gray-600.leading-relaxed
          A registered office/business in the UAE.

      / Card 3 - Required Documents
      .bg-white.border-2.border-gray-200.rounded-xl.p-8.shadow-md.hover:shadow-lg.transition-all.text-center
        .w-20.h-20.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6{style: "background-color: rgba(58, 99, 99, 0.1)"}
          %svg.w-10.h-10{fill: 'currentColor', viewBox: '0 0 24 24', style: 'color: #3A6363'}
            %path{d: 'M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8l-6-6z'}
        %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
          Required Documents
        %p.text-gray-600.leading-relaxed
          Valid commercial license and company documentation.

    .bg-gray-50.border-2.border-gray-200.rounded-xl.p-12.shadow-md
      .flex.flex-col.items-center.text-center
        .w-20.h-20.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mb-6{style: "background-color: rgba(0, 180, 216, 0.1)"}
          %svg.w-10.h-10{fill: 'none', stroke: 'currentColor', viewBox: '0 0 24 24', 'stroke-width': '2', style: 'color: #00B4D8'}
            %circle{cx: '12', cy: '12', r: '9'}
            %polyline{points: '12 6 12 12 16 14'}

        %p.text-lg.text-gray-700.leading-relaxed.max-w-2xl
          Simply submit the initial inquiry form (Your Name, Company Name, Fleet Size, Email), and your
          %span.font-semibold{style: 'color: #3A6363'} dedicated account manager
          will initiate the fast-track approval process.

    .text-center.mb-16.mt-16
      %h3.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
        Defining the Future of Mobility: Your ROI Starts Today
      %p.text-xl.text-gray-500.mb-12
        Wheels on Rent is strategically positioned to capture the exponential growth in the mobility sector. By joining us, you are not just listing a car; you are investing in a future-proof lead generation strategy that delivers quantifiable, commission-free growth. We measure our success solely by your revenue. If you own a fleet and are ready to stop losing profit to middlemen, the time to partner is now.

